working on spring security


WebSecurityConfig
      |
      | // Main security configuration class that sets up authentication and authorization rules
      | // Configures which endpoints are secure/public and sets up authentication manager
      |
CostumeUserDetails
      |
      | // Custom UserDetails implementation that wraps our User entity
      | // Provides user credentials and authorities to Spring Security
      |
CostumeUserDetailsService
      |
      | // Service that loads user from database by username (email)
      | // Called by Spring Security during authentication process
      | // Returns CostumeUserDetails object containing user information






















